They were other mothers.

26:46.063 --> 26:51.363
<i>So, I decided that if I wanted to do</i>
<i>something special with my life,</i>

26:51.693 --> 26:54.033
<i>I could go into the convent.</i>

26:54.112 --> 26:58.532
