the School Sisters of Notre Dame.

26:59.827 --> 27:02.747
[Lyn] <i>We had 51 girls that entered.</i>

27:04.289 --> 27:05.959
<i>You're measured for a habit.</i>

27:06.500 --> 27:08.380
