I could begin that journey.

27:25.519 --> 27:27.859
<i>There's, like, over 150 people</i>

27:28.105 --> 27:32.105
<i>that were between the ages of 18 and 21</i>
<i>that were there.</i>

27:32.192 --> 27:34.442
