27:34.528 --> 27:36.738
[all singing indistinctly]

27:36.822 --> 27:41.792
[Lyn] <i>We became canonical novices,</i>
<i>which meant that we were cloistered.</i>

27:42.411 --> 27:46.501
<i>It's exactly like military boot camp,</i>
<i>and it's pretty, uh, rigorous.</i>

27:47.291 --> 27:51.091
