spiritual boot camp.

27:52.504 --> 27:55.304
<i>We'd get up in the morning at 5:15,</i>

27:56.258 --> 27:57.508
<i>we'd go to Mass,</i>

27:58.302 --> 27:59.642
<i>we'd have meditation.</i>

28:01.597 --> 28:02.927
<i>We'd go to breakfast,</i>

28:03.265 --> 28:05.675
<i>and after breakfast,</i>
<i>you would have your chore to do,</i>

28:05.767 --> 28:07.057
<i>whatever you were assigned.</i>

28:08.020 --> 28:09.480
<i>Then we had classes.</i>

28:10.188 --> 28:14.318
And we had to learn
how to walk with our hands in our sleeves.

28:14.401 --> 28:19.241
